{"tid":220811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發神經！幾時開始興公開器官捐贈者身份？","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T10:54:14.000Z","uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88658eb41867a480f90ec138fdd9178699f72574","tid":220811,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，以前不嬲都唔會公開，免得不必要既麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【大愛不遲】21歲單親少女車禍離世 母捐愛女肝腎遺愛人間<br />\n<br />\n21歲少女曾蕙敏，本周一在青衣長亨邨遇車禍，搶救兩日後不治，家人將她的肝臟和腎臟捐出，令3名病人延續生命。蕙敏來自單親家庭，遺下母親和在學的胞弟，雖然兩母子生活捉襟見肘，連蕙敏的身後事亦感徬徨，但仍然願意捐出愛女的器官，遺愛人間。<br />\n<br />\n蕙敏和母親及20歲胞弟，住在將軍澳彩明苑，記者今日下午登門採訪。曾母痛失愛女，心情沉重。曾母離異多年，獨力撫養兩名子女，蕙敏中四輟學，其後修讀短期課程，至兩年前做美容化粧才穩定下來。曾母指女兒性格倔強，心地善良，據知事發時她正前往長亨邨見工。<br />\n<br />\n曾母說，蕙敏送院後隨即做手術，之後一直沒有醒過，當晚醫生指蕙敏已腦幹死亡，着家人要有心理準備，至本周三終告不治。蕙敏生前沒有填寫器官捐贈卡，醫護人員勸她捐出蕙敏的器官，幾經考慮，曾母決定捐出愛女的兩個腎和肝臟。蕙敏的胞弟正修讀高級文憑課程，母親只做兼職，生活艱難。如今蕙敏的身後事也要志願機構協助，曾母說著忍不住掉下淚來。<br />\n<br />\n車禍發生於本周一下午2時，曾蕙敏在青衣寮肚路長亨邨商場對開，遭一輛專線小巴撞倒﹝<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pVE0va﹞。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pVE0va%EF%B9%9E%E3%80%82&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1e3ac566\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2pVE0va﹞。</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170428/56625758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170428%2F56625758&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=89614ae0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170428%2F56625758&h=7e29f367\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170428/56625758</a>"},{"pid":"99b83a4659e9a1288509176b7a7bf56a0bc4ef50","tid":220811,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6cf7f633f65184cfb7413cf4f27c7cda1c4001","tid":220811,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"依家啲記者愈來愈on9<br />\n係咪dse出嚟就會請"},{"pid":"2a4999d10e9d5d16c21f8d84b5e959c4cd37a25f","tid":220811,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家啲記者愈來愈on9<br />\n係咪dse出嚟就會請</blockquote><br />\n小學下化<br />\n佢哋字都唔識多隻喎"},{"pid":"e5e05a4f285c105c4d7b1c97c673c01751ffe936","tid":220811,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"英雄化捐贈者 從而達至社會對強制捐贈冇曬反對聲音<br />\n(義士又唔見佢英雄化）"},{"pid":"d3bae81f80de34bae8c68d02a2492612194f9e56","tid":220811,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"唔公開點酬錢<br />\n<br />\n你唔見最尾寫到佢地屋企幾咁困難架咩"},{"pid":"f076186194ad00bb6afae71a3bb58b66a285f222","tid":220811,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"死左冇得打卡"},{"pid":"1298a76956a52092fc0f92f380bbdeee1c56e3dc","tid":220811,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1596b1f5ed3884c9e67cb4f277a7c55630fb471a","tid":220811,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"348a4551df321de7d3eb8e165da9f004b61fcae4","tid":220811,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b87c77d403f513a293e4dd216b4f85b89096940c","tid":220811,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T10:07:45.000Z","msg":"應該係事主同意先會公開嘅"},{"pid":"423a3562bc65b08e48c8e904e97f824f1a03cf2c","tid":220811,"uid":20270,